VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.Where\s*\(\s*["'][^"']*["']\s*\+|\.Where\s*\(\s*fmt\.Sprintf\s*\(["'][^"']*%[sv]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:\.Where\s*\(\s*"[^"]*\?|\.Where\s*\(\s*&\w+|\.Where\s*\(\s*map\[|db\.Model
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects GORM Where() calls with conditions built via string concatenation or fmt.Sprintf.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Unparameterized Where() Clause.
